Introduced Version
HOUSE BILL No. 1131
_____
DIGEST OF INTRODUCED BILL
Citations Affected: IC 25-8.
Synopsis: Licensed estheticians. Amends the definition of
"esthetician" to include certain services. Adds a definition for
"microneedling". Requires a person who provides microneedling to
provide the professional licensing agency proof of advanced training
or certification at the agency's request.
Effective: July 1, 2026.
Criswell, Teshka, Patterson
January 5, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Employment, Labor and
Pensions.
2026 IN 1131—LS 6432/DI 148

